<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie-iedge"> 
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@200;300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Black&family=Pontano+Sans&family=Source+Sans+Pro&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Domine:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">  
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="../../public/img/logopreto.png" />   
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:ital,wght@1,300&family=Sansita+Swashed:wght@300;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Depressão</title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="item-body"> 
        <ul class="nav flex-column">
            <li class="nav-item" ><img class="user" src="../../public/img/usertemplate.png"></li>
            <li><p class="user-name nav-item"><%= dados.nome %></p></li>
            <hr>   
            <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link active nav-desative" href="/user">Inicial</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link nav-desative" href="/criar-relato">Criar Relato</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link nav-desative" href="/users">Comunidade</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link nav-active" href="/perfil" tabindex="-1" aria-disabled="true">Seu Perfil</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link nav-desative" href="/logout" tabindex="-1" aria-disabled="true">Sair</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <section class="geral">
    <section class="explain">
        <div class="explain-item">
            <h2>Altere seu perfil</h2>
            <p>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Nesta página você pode modificar as informações do seu perfil. Para alterar algo, basta digitar sua senha atual, e preencher os campos que quer alterar, deixando vazios aqueles os quais você não quiser mexer.</p>
        </div>    
    </section>    
    <section class='formulario item-body center'>
        <div class="div-form">
            <form class="criar-relato" method="POST" action="/alterar-perfil">
                <p class="item-relato">Novo nome:</p>
                <input class="item-relato" name="nome" placeholder="Nome" maxlength="16" required>
                <p class="item-relato">Senha antiga:</p>
                <input class="item-relato" name="senhaantiga" placeholder="Senha antiga" required>
                <p class="item-relato">Nova senha:</p>
                <input class="item-relato text-area" name="senha" placeholder="Nova senha" required>
                <p class="item-relato">Nova e-mail:</p>
                <input class="item-relato text-area" name="email" placeholder="Novo e-mail" required>
                <button class="item-relato" type = "submit" name="btalterar">Create</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>    
</section>
    <style>
        body{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
        }
        .geral{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        nav p{
            font-family: 'Sansita Swashed', cursive;
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            
        }
        nav{
            height: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: black;
            border-radius: 0px 30px 30px 0px;
        }
        .nav-item{
            padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px;
            align-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .nav-item a {
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            border-radius: 30px;
            
        }
        .user{
            height: 100px;
            width: auto;
            
        }
        hr{
            width: 70%;
            height: 1px;
            padding: 0px;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .nav-active{
            background-color: purple;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 30px;
        }
        .nav-desative:hover{
            background-color: white;
            color: black;
            font-weight: 200;
            transition: 0.4s;
        }
        .criar-relato{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 50%;
            
        }
        .explain{
            display:flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            padding-top: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .explain-item{
            display:flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 50%;
        }
        .item-relato{
            margin: 10px;
        }
        button{
          text-shadow: none;
          border: none;
          color: white;
          padding: 16px 32px;
          text-align: center;
          text-decoration: none;
          display: inline-block;
          font-size: 16px;
          margin: 4px 2px;
          transition-duration: 0.4s;
          cursor: pointer;
          top: 72%;
          left: 50%;
          background-color: black; 
        }

        button:hover {
          background-color: purple;
          font-size: 18px;
          border-radius: 6px;
        }
        .div-form{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            
        }
        .formulario{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
    </style>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a563a889e2.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ho+j7jyWK8fNQe+A12Hb8AhRq26LrZ/JpcUGGOn+Y7RsweNrtN/tE3MoK7ZeZDyx" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>